  '',
  'Original BMW Style 407 featuring distinctive star spoke design. Introduced with F30 3 Series and carried over to F3X 4 Series models. The bicolor finish combines ferric grey base with bright turned spoke faces creating an elegant two-tone appearance. This wheel was a popular option throughout the F30/F3X generation lifecycle. Available in staggered fitment with different offsets for front and rear positions. Center cap part number 36136783536 is the standard 68mm BMW roundel design used across multiple wheel styles.',
