  '[{"value":"E36 3 Series\nE46 3 Series\nE36/7 Z3"}]',
  '[{"value":"72.6mm"}]',
  'ET47',
  '',
  'BMW Style 43 is also known as ''Star Spoke'' design. Originally designed to complement the lines of the E36, E46, and Z3 models. This wheel was part of BMW''s OEM lineup from the 1990s through early 2000s and features a classic 5-spoke star pattern that became iconic for BMW''s sporty aesthetic during this era. The design emphasizes both performance and visual appeal with its geometric spoke arrangement.',
  'Silver (Paint Code 144)',
