  'Approximately 21kg (estimated)',
  'The Jaguar Helix #5033 is a 5 split-spoke alloy wheel designed specifically for the Jaguar XF X260 generation (2015-2024). Manufactured in the UK by Jaguar, this wheel features precision forged aluminum construction and was introduced alongside the X260 XF at the 2015 New York International Auto Show. The design emphasizes elegance and strength, with the 5 split-spoke pattern providing both aesthetic appeal and structural integrity. Available in multiple factory finishes, this wheel was offered across various XF trim levels including Pure, Prestige, Portfolio, and R-Sport. The wheel uses the standard Jaguar 5x108 bolt pattern and 63.4mm center bore. Tire fitment is 245/45R18 100W. The Helix name reflects the distinctive spoke pattern that creates visual movement and dynamic appeal. Part numbers vary by finish and production period, with Pre-21MY and Post-21MY variants available.',
