  'Approximately 29 lbs (rear wheel)',
  'The Toba #5043 is a genuine Jaguar OEM wheel design featuring an elegant 5 twin-spoke pattern. Originally introduced for the X351 generation XJ in 2010, these wheels were designed in the UK by Jaguar as a factory option. The staggered setup (19x9 front, 19x10 rear) enhances the XJ''s luxury sedan profile while maintaining optimal handling characteristics. Available in multiple finishes including Chrome Polished and Sparkle Silver. The aluminum alloy construction reduces unsprung weight while providing excellent durability and strength. The wheel was produced throughout the X351''s production run from 2010-2019.',
