  '',
  '',
  'The Aerodynamic #1017 is a distinctive 10-spoke alloy wheel designed for the Jaguar XF range. This wheel embodies Jaguar''s aerodynamic design philosophy with its sleek spoke pattern optimized for airflow efficiency. Originally introduced for the first-generation XF (X250) and continued through the second-generation (X260), this wheel represents Jaguar''s commitment to combining performance with elegant aesthetics. The wheel features Jaguar''s signature Sparkle Silver finish and is manufactured from lightweight aluminum alloy. Specifically designed for diesel variants with the 2.0-liter I4 163PS engine, it was not available for all-wheel-drive configurations. The Aerodynamic designation reflects Jaguar''s focus on computational fluid dynamics (CFD) optimization in the XF''s development, where every component including wheel design was tested for aerodynamic efficiency.',
  'Sparkle Silver (standard factory finish)',
  '![[Jaguar_Aerodynamic_1017_Wheels.jpg]]',
  true
) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
