  'Cromodora Wheels S.p.A. is an Italian wheel manufacturer established in 1962, serving as an OEM supplier to prestigious manufacturers including Jaguar-Land Rover, Ferrari, and BMW. The ''JP'' designation for this specific Cromodora wheel pattern could not be verified through available documentation, suggesting it may be an internal code or informal designation. Cromodora pioneered high-pressure cast magnesium alloy wheels and later introduced flow-forming technology for lighter wheels. These 15-inch wheels represent the classic era of Jaguar wheel design, likely from the 1970s-1980s period when 15-inch wheels were common on luxury vehicles.',
  'Silver / Natural Aluminum finish',
  NULL,
  true
