  '[{"value":"57.1mm"}]',
  '+50mm',
  '',
  'Introduced in 2009 with the LP560 launch, replacing the Cassiopeia wheel as standard. Features a distinctive 5-spoke split design with kinked spokes. Standard finish was satin silver, with special diamond turned and black variants for limited editions. Used on Gallardo models from 2009-2013. The design has asymmetrical spoke rotation due to non-directional pattern.',
