  'ET28 (Front) / ET22 (Rear)',
  'Approx. 20% lighter than cast equivalents (Forged construction)',
  'The Auriga is a factory OEM forged wheel option for the Lamborghini Urus, introduced as part of the Urus wheel portfolio. Named after the constellation Auriga, it features a distinctive 10-spoke design characteristic of Lamborghini''s modern wheel aesthetics. Available in multiple factory finishes including the signature Auriga Bronze and Shiny Black. The wheel utilizes aerospace-grade 6061-T6 forged aluminum construction for superior strength-to-weight ratio. Compatible with TPMS and standard Lamborghini center caps. Front and rear wheels have different offsets to accommodate the Urus''s staggered setup. Primarily offered in 22-inch diameter, though some 21-inch variants exist in specific markets.',
