  '',
  'Lightweight forged magnesium construction - exact weight varies by size',
  'Second generation Scorpius wheel introduced in 2011 for the LP570-4 Superleggera. Manufactured by Speedline, these forged magnesium alloy wheels feature titanium wheel nuts and were specifically designed for the lightweight, track-focused Superleggera variants. The Titanium finish was standard on the Superleggera and Performante models, while high gloss black was standard on the Super Trofeo Stradale. Paint code MA622.70 confirmed by Lamborghini dealerships. Succeeded the original Scorpius design from the 2008 Superleggera.',
