  '[{"value":"72.6mm"}]',
  'ET20 (Front 8J), ET22 (Rear 9J)',
  '',
  'Exclusively designed for BMW Z8 E52 (2000-2003). Very rare wheel with staggered fitment. Features distinctive double-spoke design to complement Z8''s retro styling. Can fit other BMW models with 5x120 bolt pattern but may require center bore modifications. Original tires: 245/45 R18 (front), 275/40 R18 (rear). Also known as ''Twin-Spoke'' or ''Double-Spoke'' design. Factory finish was silver/titanium silver to match Z8''s most popular paint color.',
  'Silver/Titanium Silver (Factory), Chrome (Aftermarket)',
  '![[bmwstyle59.jpg]]',
  true
) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
