  'Approximately 18-20 lbs',
  'Official MINI OEM wheel introduced with third-generation F-series models (2014+). Seven-spoke design manufactured in the UK by MINI. Available in two factory finishes: Spectre Grey and Bright Turned with Black. Standard fitment for F55/F56/F57 chassis Cooper models. Features modern aluminum alloy construction with flow-formed manufacturing process. Compatible with TPMS sensors. Design emphasizes lightweight construction while maintaining structural integrity for performance applications.',
