  'BMW Style 265 was specifically designed for the E70 X5 and E71 X6 models, featuring an Individual V Spoke design. This was a staggered wheel setup with different front and rear sizes and offsets. The E71 X6 and X5M models uniquely used different center bore dimensions front to rear (74.0mm front, 72.5mm rear), unlike other BMW models which typically use consistent center bores. Production ran from 2007-2013 coinciding with the E70/E71 platform lifecycle. The wheel design emphasized performance and luxury aesthetics matching the SAV (Sports Activity Vehicle) concept BMW introduced with these models.',
