  'BMW Style 260 (also designated as Style 260M for M3 applications) features the iconic M Double Spoke design with 10 spokes arranged in twin-spoke pairs. Originally designed for the E90/E92/E93 M3, this wheel represents BMW''s high-performance wheel design philosophy. The wheel utilizes a staggered setup with different widths and offsets front to rear for optimal handling characteristics. The aggressive offsets (ET29/ET23) position the wheels more outboard for improved track width and stance. Available primarily in Ferric Grey finish with possible additional BMW OEM color options.',
