  'Lightweight forged construction - approximately 20-22 lbs per wheel',
  'Introduced in 2008 as the standard wheel for the E90 M3. The Style 220 features BMW''s distinctive M Double Spoke design with forged aluminum construction. Each of the 5 main spokes is split/doubled, creating a dynamic 10-spoke visual appearance. Originally available in silver/gunmetal finish, with special Jet Black version offered later. Designed specifically for high-performance applications with lightweight forged construction to reduce unsprung weight. Compatible with 245/35/19 front and 265/35/19 rear tires as recommended by BMW.',
