  'Approx. 7-9 kg (15.4-19.8 lbs) depending on size',
  'Classic star-spoke design introduced in the late 1980s as part of BMW''s first-generation style wheel lineup. Known officially as ''Star Spoke'' design, featuring distinctive radiating spokes from center hub. Available in multiple sizes with different bolt patterns to accommodate various BMW chassis. The 15" versions typically used 4x100 PCD for E30 models, while 17" staggered sets used 5x120 PCD for larger chassis like E32/E34. Manufactured using cast aluminum construction with powder-coated finish for durability.',
