  'BMW Style 78 features a distinctive 10 Y-spoke cross design. Available in both 17" one-piece and 18" two-piece composite (bolted) configurations. The 17" version was standard on Z3 Sport models with staggered fitment (7.5J front, 8.5J rear). The rare 18" bolted split-rim version was offered as an optional upgrade for Z4 models. Two-piece construction allows for refinishing and repair. Originally manufactured by BBS for BMW with cross-spoke pattern reminiscent of classic wire wheels but in modern aluminum construction.',
