  'Front: 11.27kg (24.8 lbs), Rear: 11.9kg (26.2 lbs)',
  'BMW Style 640 (also designated 640M for M Performance winter variant) is a specialized winter wheel design introduced around 2015-2016. Features staggered sizing with flow-forming aluminum construction. Designed specifically for BMW M Performance vehicles (F87 M2, F80 M3, F82/F83 M4) as OEM winter wheel option. The V-spoke design provides optimal winter performance while maintaining BMW''s aesthetic standards. Compatible with run-flat tires and includes TPMS (RDCi) integration. Not suitable for vehicles with carbon-ceramic brakes.',
