  '',
  'BMW Style 108 is a rare European-market two-piece wheel exclusively designed for the BMW E85 Z4 (2003-2008). Manufactured by BBS for BMW, this staggered wheel set features a refined 5-spoke design with a two-piece construction using titanium bolts. Originally available as an optional upgrade from the standard 17-inch wheels, the Style 108 was part of BMW''s premium wheel lineup. The wheel features a distinctive silver finish with machined lip detailing. Production was limited to the E85/E86 Z4 generation, making these wheels highly sought after by enthusiasts. The two-piece design allows for different finishes and customization options. These wheels are considered among the best-looking OEM BMW wheels and maintain excellent collectibility due to their limited production run and exclusive Z4 application.',
  'Silver with machined lip (factory finish)',
  '![[bmwstyle108.jpg]]',
