  'BMW Style 560 is a 10-spoke aluminum alloy wheel introduced with the F48 X1 LCI facelift in 2019. Originally designed for the X1 F48 LCI, this wheel features a distinctive V-spoke pattern with Reflex Silver finish. The design became part of BMW''s updated styling language for the 2019+ model year refresh. Compatible with multiple BMW and MINI models sharing the UKL2 platform. Production began in 2019 and continues as standard equipment on various BMW models.',
