  '12.62 kg front, 13.23 kg rear',
  'BMW Style 199 is a 5-spoke Star Spoke design exclusive to the E90 generation 3 Series. Introduced in 2005 with the E90 launch, this wheel was available through the entire production run of the 5th generation 3 Series (2005-2013). The staggered fitment (8" front, 9" rear) provides optimal handling characteristics. Standard finish is silver painted aluminum, though BMW Individual color options were available. The wheel is designed for run-flat tire compatibility with EH2 humps. Production ceased with the introduction of the F30 3 Series in 2012-2013.',
