  '20" M Performance: Front ET36, Rear ET40. 18-19" versions vary by application',
  'Forged aluminum construction provides approximately 20% weight reduction compared to cast wheels. M Performance versions are significantly lighter due to forged construction.',
  'BMW Style 405 is part of BMW''s M Double Spoke design family. Originally designed for F-generation models starting around 2012-2013. Available in both standard and M Performance variants. M Performance versions feature forged construction, BMW M logo, and premium finishes. Compatible with RDC (Tire Pressure Monitoring) systems. Standard wheel for F20 1 Series, F22 2 Series, F30 3 Series, F32/F33/F36 4 Series, and F34 3 Series GT.',
  'Standard finishes include Sheen finish, Schwarz matt (Matte Black). M Performance versions available in Orbit Grey with gloss-lathed face, Jet Black with polished/diamond-cut face, and various bicolour combinations.',
  '![[bmwstyle405.webp]]',
  true
) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
