  'BMW Style 85 ''Parallelspeiche'' (parallel spoke) wheel design featuring a classic 5-spoke pattern. Available in both 17" and 18" diameters with staggered fitments. Originally introduced in the mid-1990s for the E36 3-Series and later extended to E46, E39, and Z3 models. The design name ''Parallelspeiche'' refers to the parallel arrangement of the five spokes radiating from the center. Standard silver finish with high-quality aluminum alloy construction. Compatible across multiple BMW chassis generations making it a popular OEM wheel choice. Permanently discontinued by BMW but remains sought after by enthusiasts for its timeless design and broad compatibility.',
