  'ET20, ET41, ET46',
  '15-22 lbs (varies by size and construction)',
  'BMW Style 42 wheels were manufactured by BBS and featured both 1-piece (16") and 2-piece (17", 18") constructions. Known as ''Cross Spoke'' design, these wheels were original equipment on E36 3-Series, E46 3-Series, E39 5-Series, E38 7-Series, and Z3 models. The 2-piece versions use titanium bolts and feature machined outer lips. Different center bore sizes were used depending on the application - 72.6mm for E36/E46/Z3 and 74.1mm for E39. Production spanned the 1990s through early 2000s. These wheels are highly sought after by BMW enthusiasts and are considered among the best OEM wheel designs BMW has offered.',
  'Silver with machined face, polished lip, clear coat finish. Various refinish options available.',
  '![[bmwstyle42.jpg]]',
  true
