  'Lightweight forged construction (specific weight TBD)',
  'Iconic BMW multi-spoke design from the 1990s era. Originally designed for E38 7-Series but widely compatible across BMW''s luxury sedan lineup. Forged aluminum construction provides lightweight strength and improved performance. The multi-spoke pattern enhances brake cooling and creates sophisticated visual appeal. Represents BMW''s 1990s design philosophy balancing form and function. Popular choice for restoration to original specifications. The polished finish captures light dynamically, complementing the smooth lines of larger BMW sedans. Perfect balance between comfort and performance for the era.',
