  '[{"value":"E53 X5"}]',
  '[{"value":"72.6mm"}]',
  'ET45, ET30',
  'Approximately 30-35 lbs per wheel (varies by size)',
  'BMW Style 87 is a distinctive 5-spoke "Star Spoke" design introduced in 2000-2001 specifically for the BMW X5 E53, initially featured on the high-performance 4.6is model. This wheel was BMW''s first 20-inch OEM wheel design for SUVs, representing a significant step in BMW''s sporty SUV aesthetic. Available in staggered fitment: 9.5J x 20 ET45 (front) and 10.5J x 20 ET30 (rear). The design features bold, straight spokes emanating from the center, creating a dynamic five-pointed star pattern. Originally equipped with larger brake packages on 4.6is models. The wheel became an iconic design element that influenced future BMW SUV wheel styling. Production continued through the E53 generation (1999-2006) and became highly sought after by enthusiasts for its clean, motorsport-inspired appearance and substantial presence.',
  'Silver, Anthracite, available in various BMW factory finishes',
  '![[bmwstyle87.jpg]]',
  true
) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
