  '12.63 kg (27.8 lbs) per wheel',
  'PREMIUM M SPORT WHEEL: Originally equipped on E92 335i M Sport Package (2007-2013). M Double Spoke design with 10 paired spokes. STAGGERED SETUP with different front/rear sizes optimized for performance. MANUFACTURING: Made in Italy to BMW OEM standards. FINISH: High-quality metallic silver with multi-stage coating process. COMPATIBILITY: Direct fit for all E9X 3-Series (except M3), E84 X1, and E46 with proper 5x120 fitment. PERFORMANCE: Designed for M Sport brake packages with optimized cooling. WEIGHT: 12.63kg per wheel, approximately 5-6 lbs heavier than BBS alternatives but premium BMW quality. MARKET: Originally $645 MSRP per wheel, commonly refurbished and resold. TECHNICAL: BMW standard 72.6mm center bore, 88 ft-lbs lug torque specification.',
