  '[{"value":"Mercedes-Benz - W169: A-Class"}]',
  '[{"value":"66.6mm"}]',
  'ET43',
  '',
  'Standard OEM 5-spoke wheel for Mercedes-Benz A-Class W169 (2005-2012). Cast aluminum construction with titanium silver finish. Part of base equipment for A-Class models during W169 production run. Compatible with tire sizes 195/55R16 to 205/55R16. Produced at Mercedes-Benz facilities with typical offset range ET40-50 for W169 chassis.',
  '9765 Titanium Silver',
