  '[{"value":"66.6mm"}]',
  'ET43 (17"), ET43 (18")',
  '',
  'Standard OEM 5-spoke wheel for W221 S-Class and C216 CL-Class. The 17" variant was commonly referred to as the ''diplomat'' wheel due to its comfort-oriented design. Recommended tire sizes: 245/55R17 (17") and 255/45R18 (18"). Both variants share the same offset (ET43) but different widths. Part of the initial W221 launch wheel options from 2005-2009, with continued availability through the 2009 facelift until 2013.',
  'Titanium Gray (Titansilber)',
  '![[Screenshot_2025-04-08_at_14.38.03.png]]',
