  'ET43',
  '',
  'Genuine Mercedes-Benz OEM 5-spoke wheel designed specifically for the W221 S-Class generation (2005-2013). Part of the standard wheel options available from factory. Features classic 5-spoke design with titanium gray finish. Recommended tire size 255/45 R18. Also compatible with C216 CL-Class. Available in various sizes from 17-20 inches across the W221 lineup.',
