  'ET60',
  'Lightweight option (0 weight penalty vs base)',
  'The Aurora was a premium 17-inch wheel option primarily for the Jaguar S-Type VDP (Vanden Plas) luxury variant. It was one of the lighter wheel options available, with no weight penalty compared to the base wheels. Standard tire size was 235/50R17. The wheel featured Jaguar''s signature high positive offset design (ET60) which was critical for proper handling and suspension geometry. Also compatible with X-Type and XF models. Part of Jaguar''s classic named wheel collection alongside Juno, Triton, Valencia, and others. Production period: approximately 2005-2008 for S-Type applications.',
  'Silver (Powder Coat Silver finish)',
