  'Front: ET48.4, Rear: ET66 (optimized for CLA C174 suspension geometry)',
  'Approximately 26-28 lbs per wheel (typical for 18x7.5J AMG wheels), offering reduced unsprung weight for improved handling and fuel efficiency',
  'Third-generation CLA (C174) launched March 2025. Genuine Mercedes-AMG wheels with staggered setup for enhanced performance. Features 5-spoke design optimized for brake cooling and aerodynamics. Manufactured using precision casting process with extensive Mercedes-Benz quality testing including salt spray and climate testing. Compatible with CLA 250+ and CLA 350 4MATIC models. Standard equipment on AMG Line trim levels. Wheels include ABE certification requiring no vehicle registration modifications in Germany.',
  'Tantalum grey high-sheen finish - A premium metallic grey finish with high-gloss treatment that provides excellent durability and corrosion resistance. Also available in titanium grey and high-gloss black finishes.',
  '![[Mercedes-Benz5SpokeCLA.jpg]]',
  true
